## CONSTRAINTS & TRUST LEVELS

> Read before relying on any data in this document. `✓` = verified from primary source. `⚠️` = assumption or secondary source — verify before acting.

| # | Item | Status |
|---|---|---|
| C1 | Open API is in **beta** | ⚠️ Monitor for breaking changes |
| C2 | Platform OAuth is **invite-only** | ✓ Use Basic Auth for single-shop automation |
| C3 | API base URL is `https://api.fourthwall.com` | ✓ (not `openapi.fourthwall.com` — that is wrong) |
| C4 | API path versioning is **inconsistent** | ⚠️ Auth guide: `/v1/`, Shop spec: `/v1.0/`, Memberships: `/v1.1/` — verify each path |
| C5 | Webhook signature header is `X-Fourthwall-Hmac-SHA256` | ✓ (not `X-Fourthwall-Signature` — that silently fails) |
| C6 | Webhook delivery is **at-least-once, not exactly-once** | ✓ Deduplicate on event `id` field |
| C7 | Webhook ordering is **not guaranteed** | ✓ `ORDER_UPDATED` may arrive before `ORDER_PLACED` — build order-agnostic handlers |
| C8 | Webhook delivery is **not guaranteed** | ✓ Implement reconciliation polling for data requiring consistency |
| C9 | Content-gating **is supported** | ✓ Memberships API has full per-post access control |
| C10 | Credential creation requires **SUPER ADMIN** role | ✓ Shop owner = SUPER ADMIN by default |
| C11 | `state` param on Posts endpoint is **required** | ✓ Missing = 400 error. Must pass `Published`, `Scheduled`, or `All` |
| C12 | Subscription webhook names differ across docs | ⚠️ Older docs: `SUBSCRIPTION_CREATED/DELETED` · Current API: `SUBSCRIPTION_PURCHASED/EXPIRED` — treat as equivalent |
| C13 | Twitch Gifting webhooks are **beta** | ⚠️ Require StreamElements + separate Gifting App setup |
| C14 | Fee and economics data | ⚠️ Verify at fourthwall.com before financial decisions |
| C15 | Merch product specs | ⚠️ Verify dimensions at help.fourthwall.com before production |

