| Component | Free Plan | Pro ($19/mo) |
|---|---|---|
| Memberships | 5% | 5% |
| Digital products | 5% | 0% |
| Physical products | 0% | 0% |
| CC processing (domestic) | 2.9% + $0.30 | same |
| PayPal (domestic) | 3.49% + $0.49 | same |
| Payout | $0 | $0 |
| Apple IAP surcharge | None (PWA model) | None |
| Sales tax | Merchant of Record — handled | same |

