## 4. API SURFACE

Three APIs. Rate limit applies to Platform and Memberships APIs.

```
RATE LIMIT    100 requests / 10-second rolling window
BEHAVIOR      Excess requests are DELAYED, not rejected (no 429)
RECOMMENDATION Pace below 10 req/sec
```

| API | Base URL | Auth | Version prefix |
|---|---|---|---|
| Platform | `https://api.fourthwall.com` | Basic Auth / OAuth | `/open-api/v1.0/` `⚠️ C4` |
| Memberships | `https://api.fourthwall.com` | Basic Auth / OAuth | `/open-api/v1.1/memberships/` |
| Storefront | `https://storefront-api.fourthwall.com` | Storefront token | `/v1/` |

OpenAPI specs:
```
Platform   https://docs.fourthwall.com/open-api-docs/open-api.json
Storefront https://docs.fourthwall.com/open-api-docs/storefront.json
```

### 4.1 Platform API Endpoints `✓ Partially verified`

```
GET    /open-api/v1.0/shops/current                       ✓ spec verified
GET    /open-api/v1.0/orders                              ⚠️ path inferred
GET    /open-api/v1.0/orders/{id}
GET    /open-api/v1.0/products
GET    /open-api/v1.0/products/{id}
POST   /open-api/v1.0/products
PUT    /open-api/v1.0/products/{id}
GET    /open-api/v1.0/supporters
GET    /open-api/v1.0/supporters/{id}
GET    /open-api/v1.0/memberships
GET    /open-api/v1.0/subscriptions
GET    /open-api/v1.0/mailing-lists
POST   /open-api/v1.0/mailing-lists/{id}/subscribe
POST   /open-api/v1.0/webhooks                            ✓ spec verified
GET    /open-api/v1.0/webhooks
GET    /open-api/v1.0/webhooks/{id}
PUT    /open-api/v1.0/webhooks/{id}
DELETE /open-api/v1.0/webhooks/{id}
PUT    /open-api/v1.0/streaming/start                     ✓ gifting guide
PUT    /open-api/v1.0/gifting/draw/{drawId}/finish        ✓ gifting guide
```

Shop response object:
```json
{ "id": "00aa4abd-...", "name": "string", "domain": "string", "publicDomain": "string" }
```

### 4.2 Storefront API Endpoints `✓ Partially verified`

```
Base: https://storefront-api.fourthwall.com/v1
Auth: ?storefront_token=TOKEN on every request

GET  /v1/shop
GET  /v1/collections
GET  /v1/collections/{collection_slug}/products
GET  /v1/products/{product_slug}
POST /v1/carts                                body: { "currency": "USD" }
POST /v1/carts/{cart_id}/items                body: { "variantId": "...", "quantity": 1 }
GET  /v1/carts/{cart_id}
```

Key Storefront constraints:
- **No list-all-products endpoint.** Use `/collections/all/products` — the `all` collection contains every public product.
- **Payments cannot be processed through API.** Redirect to Fourthwall-hosted checkout: `https://{shop}.fourthwall.com/checkout/?cartCurrency=USD&cartId={cart_id}`
- **Cart ID must be stored client-side.** API does not persist carts — loss of `cart_id` requires a new cart.
- **Cart operations require `variantId`**, not product ID. Retrieve from product endpoints.
- **Storefront token is visible in client code** if using a static frontend. Mitigate with a backend proxy.

Pagination:
```
?page=0&size=50
Response: { results: Product[], paging: { hasNextPage: boolean } }
Continue until paging.hasNextPage === false
```

### 4.3 Memberships API (Posts) `✓`

```
Base URL   https://api.fourthwall.com
Prefix     /open-api/v1.1/memberships/
Scope      memberships_read · memberships_write
```

List posts:
```
GET /open-api/v1.1/memberships/posts

Required: state = Published | Scheduled | All  (see C11)
Optional: page · limit · search_query · types[] · ids[] · tags_ids[]
types[]: Text · Poll · Image · Audio · Video
```

Access control object on every post:
```json
{
  "access": {
    "type": "Public | FreeMembers | FreeAndPaidMembers | MembersOnly | Plans",
    "tiers": [{ "id": 123 }]
  }
}
```

Post types: Text · Poll · Image · Audio · Video · VideoEmbed (YouTube, Streamable, Vimeo)

Post statuses:
```
resources: None | Created | Processing | Completed | Errored
post:      Created | Ready | Live | Finished | Archived
schedule:  None | Asap | Future | Done
```

