## 5. WEBHOOKS

The highest-value Fourthwall integration surface. Every stream alert, Discord role assignment, and CRM update flows from here.

### 5.1 Setup

Dashboard: Settings → For Developers → Webhooks → Add URL → Select events

API (programmatic):
```bash
curl -u "user:pass" -X POST "https://api.fourthwall.com/open-api/v1.0/webhooks" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"url": "https://your-server.com/hook", "allowedTypes": ["ORDER_PLACED"]}'
```

Response — store `secret` immediately:
```json
{ "id": "wcon_...", "url": "...", "allowedTypes": [...], "secret": "e3f93c7c-..." }
```

### 5.2 Event Envelope (all events share this structure)

```json
{
  "testMode": false,
  "id": "weve_geAva6c1RAuyb9HQxbSlmA",
  "webhookId": "wcon_P-VkRfmJTBaC6_Tst22cew",
  "shopId": "sh_7ad0c438-beda-4779-a885-0dc325a755c1",
  "type": "ORDER_PLACED",
  "apiVersion": "V1_BETA",
  "createdAt": "2023-07-12T15:05:11.078089+00:00",
  "data": {}
}
```

Key fields: `id` = dedup key · `testMode` = filter test events · `type` = determines `data` shape

### 5.3 Event Types

| Event | Trigger |
|---|---|
| `ORDER_PLACED` | Any store purchase |
| `ORDER_UPDATED` | Order status change |
| `GIFT_PURCHASE` | Gift order placed |
| `DONATION` | One-time donation |
| `PRODUCT_CREATED` | New product added |
| `PRODUCT_UPDATED` | Product edited |
| `SUBSCRIPTION_PURCHASED` | New membership |
| `SUBSCRIPTION_CHANGED` | Tier change |
| `SUBSCRIPTION_EXPIRED` | Cancelled or lapsed |
| `THANK_YOU_SENT` | Thank-you message sent |
| `NEWSLETTER_SUBSCRIBED` | Mailing list signup |
| `GIFT_DRAW_STARTED` | Twitch gift draw opened `⚠️ C13` |
| `GIFT_DRAW_ENDED` | Twitch gift draw completed `⚠️ C13` |

### 5.4 Signature Verification `✓`

```
HEADER    X-Fourthwall-Hmac-SHA256  (not X-Fourthwall-Signature — see C5)
APPS HDR  X-Fourthwall-Hmac-Apps-SHA256  (Platform Apps only)
ALGORITHM HMAC-SHA256(secret, raw_body) → base64 → compare
```

```python
import hmac, hashlib, base64

def verify(data: bytes, header: str, secret: str) -> bool:
    digest = hmac.new(secret.encode(), data, hashlib.sha256).digest()
    return hmac.compare_digest(base64.b64encode(digest), header.encode())
```

### 5.5 Delivery Policy `✓`

```
RESPONSE    Return 200 OK immediately — do heavy work async
TIMEOUT     2000ms max before marked failed
RETRY       5 attempts · 5-second timeout per attempt
ORDERING    Not guaranteed (see C7)
DELIVERY    At-least-once — deduplicate on event id (see C6)
GUARANTEE   Not guaranteed — reconcile with Platform API polling (see C8)
TESTING     Dashboard → Webhooks → "Send test notification" → fires with testMode: true
```

### 5.6 Recommended Webhook Flows (Streaming + CRM)

```
SUBSCRIPTION_PURCHASED
  → Verify X-Fourthwall-Hmac-SHA256
  → Fire on-stream alert (StreamElements / Streamlabs / Streamer.bot)
  → Discord: post welcome embed to tier channel
  → Notion/CRM: create member row
  → Discord bot: assign tier role

SUBSCRIPTION_EXPIRED
  → Discord bot: remove tier role
  → Notion/CRM: update member status → lapsed

ORDER_PLACED
  → Fire on-stream merch alert
  → Notion/CRM: log to fulfillment tracker

DONATION
  → Fire on-stream alert
  → Log to revenue tracker
```

### 5.7 Twitch Gifting Flow `⚠️ C13`

```
SETUP   Dashboard → Apps → Twitch → StreamElements gifting → Enable
        Create webhooks for GIFT_DRAW_STARTED + GIFT_DRAW_ENDED

START STREAM
PUT /open-api/v1.0/streaming/start
{ "services": [{ "type": "TWITCH", "broadcasterId": "...", "broadcasterLogin": "..." }] }

FINISH DRAW
PUT /open-api/v1.0/gifting/draw/{drawId}/finish
{ "participants": [{ "service": "TWITCH", "userId": "...", "userName": "..." }] }

NOTE    Draws not finished within configured time + 1 min auto-close with no winner
NOTE    Gifted memberships can only be redeemed by users NOT already members
```

