## 11. LAUNCH CHECKLIST

### Minimum Viable Setup

- [ ] 1 paid tier created
- [ ] 1–3 clear perks assigned
- [ ] Welcome post created
- [ ] 1 public post live
- [ ] Memberships added to homepage and menu
- [ ] Annual plan enabled
- [ ] Launch discount or promo code ready
- [ ] Discord perk configured (if community matters)
- [ ] Member-only product or discount configured (if merch matters)

### Streaming Integration

- [ ] Webhook endpoint deployed and tested
- [ ] Signature verification live (`X-Fourthwall-Hmac-SHA256`)
- [ ] Test event fired from Dashboard → Webhooks → Send test notification
- [ ] Stream alert tool connected (StreamElements / Streamlabs / Streamer.bot)
- [ ] Alert fires for `ORDER_PLACED`, `DONATION`, `SUBSCRIPTION_PURCHASED`
- [ ] Discord native integration enabled (if not using custom bot)
- [ ] Twitch Gifting configured if streaming live on Twitch

### Merch Production

- [ ] Master canvas created at 15,000 × 9,000px, 300 PPI, RGB
- [ ] Composition planned for landscape, square, and portrait crops
- [ ] Sublimation colors pushed +10–15% brightness/saturation
- [ ] CMYK converted from RGB master (never painted in CMYK)
- [ ] 100% zoom QA for artifacts before production
- [ ] Files named per convention
- [ ] Layered source file included in delivery

